o entities, no controllers, no services, no repositories.\n\n**Backend package.json** contents:\n```json\n{\n  \"name\": \"backend\",\n  \"version\": \"0.1.0\",\n  \"private\": true,\n  \"scripts\": {\n    \"typecheck\": \"tsc --noEmit\",\n    \"build\": \"tsc\"\n  },\n  \"dependencies\": {\n    \"@nestjs/common\": \"^10.3.0\",\n    \"@nestjs/core\": \"^10.3.0\",\n    \"@nestjs/typeorm\": \"^10.0.2\",\n    \"class-transformer\": \"^0.5.1\",\n    \"class-validator\": \"^0.14.1\",\n    \"reflect-metadata\": \"^0.2.2\",\n    \"rxjs\": \"^7.8.1\",\n    \"typeorm\": \"^0.3.20\"\n  },\n  \"devDependencies\": {\n    \"@types/node\": \"^20.12.7\",\n    \"typescript\": \"^5.4.5\"\n  }\n}\n```\n\nNote: NestJS 10.x in package.json but CLAUDE.md says 11; TypeScript 5.4.x in package.json but CLAUDE.md says 5.7+.\n\n---\n\n## 3. `backend/src/core/` — Does NOT Exist\n\nNo base classes, guards, decorators, filters, interceptors, or pipes exist yet. These all need to be built from scratch following the patterns in the architecture guides.\n\n---\n\n## 4. DTO Files — None Exist\n\nNo DTO files were found anywhere under `backend/` (glob for `**/*.dto.*` returned zero results).\n\n---\n\n## 5. Routing & Controllers Guide (`.claude/nestjs/guides/routing-and-controllers.md`)\n\n**Full file returned above (929 lines).** Key patterns:\n\n### Controller Golden Rule\nControllers should ONLY:\n- Define routes with decorators (`@Get`, `@Post`, etc.)\n- Extract request data (`@Param`, `@Body`, `@Query`)\n- Delegate to services\n- Return responses (wrapped automatically)\n\n### BaseController Pattern (MANDATORY)\nAll controllers MUST extend `BaseController<T, CreateDto, UpdateDto>`. This provides automatic CRUD:\n- `POST /` — create\n- `GET /` — findAll (with pagination)\n- `GET /:id` — findOne\n- `PATCH /:id` — update\n- `DELETE /:id` — remove\n\n### Key Decorators\n- `@Public()` — bypass authentication (from `src/core/decorators`)\n- `@Roles('admin')` — role-based access (from `src/core/decorators`)\n- `@CurrentUser()` — get authenticated user (from `src/core/decorators`)\n- `@ApiSwagger({ resourceName, operation, responseDto })` — Swagger docs (from `src/core/decorators`)\n\n### Mandatory Rules\n- Controller size limit: **200 lines** (split into sub-controllers if exceeded)\n- Swagger (`@ApiOperation` and `@ApiResponse`) on **EVERY** method\n- Rate limiting (`@Throttle`) on public auth endpoints\n- Delete returns **204** (`@HttpCode(HttpStatus.NO_CONTENT)`)\n\n### Custom Decorators Reference\n```typescript\n@Public()       // Skips JwtAuthGuard\n@Roles('admin') // Requires specific roles\n@CurrentUser()  // Injects IJwtPayload from token\n@ApiSwagger()   // Auto Swagger docs\n```\n\n---\n\n## 6. Validation Patterns Guide (`.claude/nestjs/guides/validation-patterns.md`)\n\n**Full file returned above (833 lines).** Key patterns:\n\n### DTO Organization\n- Location: `src/modules/[module]/dto/`\n- Naming: `Create[Entity]Dto`, `Update[Entity]Dto`, `[Entity]ResponseDto`, `[Entity]QueryDto`\n- Update DTOs MUST use `PartialType(Create[Entity]Dto)` (not duplicate fields)\n- Swagger `@ApiProperty()` on EVERY field — no exceptions\n- `@ApiPropertyOptional()` for optional fields\n\n### Common Validation Decorators\n- Strings: `@IsString()`, `@IsEmail()`, `@IsNotEmpty()`, `@MinLength()`, `@MaxLength()`, `@Matches()`\n- Numbers: `@IsNumber()`, `@IsInt()`, `@IsPositive()`, `@Min()`, `@Max()`\n- Booleans: `@IsBoolean()`\n- Dates: `@IsDate()` + `@Type(() => Date)` for transformation\n- Arrays: `@IsArray()`, `@ArrayNotEmpty()`, `@ArrayMinSize()`, `@ArrayMaxSize()`\n- Enums: `@IsEnum(EnumType)`\n- Nested: `@ValidateNested()` + `@Type(() => NestedClass)`\n- Conditional: `@ValidateIf((o) => condition)`\n- Optional: `@IsOptional()`\n\n### Global ValidationPipe (in main.ts)\n```typescript\nnew ValidationPipe({\n    whitelist: true,              // Strip non-DTO properties\n    forbidNonWhitelisted: true,   // Error on extra properties\n    transform: true,              // Auto-transform to DTO class\n    transformOptions: {\n        enableImplicitConversion: true,\n    },\n})\n```\n\n### MANDATORY: I18nHelper\nCustom validation messages MUST use `I18nHelper.t('validation.xxx')` — no hardcoded strings.\n\n---\n\n## 7. PROJECT_KNOWLEDGE.md — Full Content (322 lines)\n\n**Full file returned above.** Key domain model summary:\n\n### User Roles\n| Role | Permissions |\n|------|------------|\n| **Guest** | `browse_properties`, `view_property_details` |\n| **Renter** | `browse_properties`, `view_property_details`, `save_favorites`, `submit_inquiries` |\n| **Admin** | `manage_properties`, `manage_users`, `view_inquiries`, `respond_to_inquiries` |\n\n### Core Features (that need API endpoints)\n\n**Authentication:**\n- Login (email + password) → JWT httpOnly cookies\n- Registration (self-service, default Renter role)\n- Token refresh (rotation)\n- Logout (clears cookies)\n- Password reset (forgot/reset flow)\n\n**Renter Features:**\n1. Property Search — search by location, filter by price/beds/type, paginated results\n2. Property Detail — full property info with photos, amenities, Google Map, favorite toggle\n3. Favorites Management — view/remove saved properties\n4. Submit Inquiry — contact form (name, email, phone, message) on property detail\n\n**Admin Features:**\n1. Admin Dashboard — overview stats (total properties, inquiries, recent activity)\n2. Property Management (CRUD) — create, edit, soft-delete, multi-photo upload\n3. Inquiry Management — view, filter, mark read, respond\n4. User Management — list renters, view details, suspend/reactivate\n\n### Domain Entities (from Glossary)\n- **Property** — title, description, price, address, bedrooms, bathrooms, property_type, amenities, photos\n- **Property Type** — apartment, house, condo, townhouse, studio\n- **Inquiry** — name, email, phone (optional), message, status (new/read/responded), linked to Property\n- **Favorites** — many-to-many: User ↔ Property\n- **User** — name, email, password, phone (optional), role\n- **Amenity** — parking, laundry, gym, pool, air conditioning\n\n### Architecture Requirements\n- 4-layer: Controller → Service → Repository → Entity\n- ALL layers extend base classes (`BaseController`, `BaseService`, `BaseRepository`, `BaseEntity`)\n- JWT via httpOnly cookies (access: 1h, refresh: 7d)\n- Soft delete (`deleted_at`) for properties and users\n- UUID primary keys\n- Pagination on all list endpoints (default: 20, max: 100)\n\n---\n\n## Additional Architecture Guides Read\n\n### Architecture Overview (`.claude/nestjs/guides/architecture-overview.md`) — 840 lines\nConfirms the full directory structure that needs to be built:\n```\nbackend/src/\n├── core/\n│   ├── base/          # BaseEntity, BaseRepository, BaseService, BaseController\n│   ├── decorators/    # @Public, @Roles, @CurrentUser, @ApiSwagger\n│   ├── guards/        # JwtAuthGuard, RolesGuard\n│   ├── filters/       # HttpExceptionFilter\n│   ├── interceptors/  # TransformInterceptor, LoggingInterceptor\n│   └── pipes/         # ValidationPipe\n├── modules/           # Feature modules (5 files per module + dtos/)\n├── infrastructure/    # mail, s3, token, logging\n├── database/          # migrations, seeders\n├── common/enums/      # Centralized enums\n├── config/            # UnifiedConfig\n├── i18n/              # en/, ko/ translation.json\n└── main.ts\n```\n\n### PROHIBITED Patterns (Gate-Enforced)\n- Controller without `extends BaseController`\n- Service without `extends BaseService`\n- `@InjectRepository(Entity)` directly in services (must use custom repository class)\n- `createQueryBuilder()` in services (must be in repository layer only)\n\n---\n\n## Summary: Current State vs. What Needs Building\n\n| Component | Current State | Needs |\n|-----------|--------------|-------|\n| `backend/src/` | Does not exist | Full directory structure |\n| `backend/src/core/base/` | Does not exist | BaseEntity, BaseRepository, BaseService, BaseController |\n| `backend/src/core/decorators/` | Does not exist | @Public, @Roles, @CurrentUser, @ApiSwagger |\n| `backend/src/core/guards/` | Does not exist | JwtAuthGuard, RolesGuard |\n| `backend/src/core/filters/` | Does not exist | HttpExceptionFilter |\n| `backend/src/core/interceptors/` | Does not exist | TransformInterceptor, LoggingInterceptor |\n| `backend/src/modules/` | Does not exist | auth/, users/, properties/, inquiries/, favorites/ |\n| DTOs | None | Create/Update/Response/Query DTOs per entity |\n| Entities | None | User, Property, PropertyImage, Amenity, Inquiry, Favorite |\n| `PROJECT_API.md` | Does not exist | Needs creation (current pipeline node) |\n| `PROJECT_DATABASE.md` | Does not exist | Needs creation (pending pipeline node) |\n| `PROJECT_API_INTEGRATION.md` | Does not exist | Needs creation (pending pipeline node) |\n\nThe project is at the **PRD phase**, with `generate-api-doc` as the active node. The backend has zero source code — everything needs to be built from scratch following the patterns documented in `.claude/nestjs/guides/`.\n</task_result>","metadata":{"parentSessionId":"ses_1c15d7206ffeThylbmzs3dPCTB","sessionId":"ses_1c15d2f5effel2ltMxn9iEE0Ab","model":{"modelID":"deepseek-v4-pro","providerID":"opencode-go"},"truncated":false},"title":"Explore backend patterns","time":{"start":1779167318181,"end":1779167500081}},"id":"prt_e3ea2acc1001s0gwFmo1fnEehM","sessionID":"ses_1c15d7206ffeThylbmzs3dPCTB","messageID":"msg_e3ea292700018MYTsoYWk04MrP"}}
